1. Changelog
------------
This is a non-exhaustive (but still near complete) changelog for
Mambo 4.5, including beta and release candidate versions.
Our thanks to all those people who've contributed bug reports and
code fixes.

Legend:

# -> Bug Fix
+ -> Addition
! -> Change
- -> Removed
! -> Note

06-Oct-2004 Phil Taylor (Expo)
